      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still carries a great shine, though you'll find a few minor, age-appropriate blemishes like small stone chips on the front bumper and a couple of light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
